{"tid":1814812,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"期待手持牛餐肉就有西屌嘅日子","createTime":"2020-01-07T05:34:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T08:32:56.000Z","uid":152147,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d38e1cb61e807a057d19fe34870194e12c676bf0","tid":1814812,"uid":152147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T05:34:33.000Z","msg":"2012又好,927又好,UFO又好,出老解又好,核炸伊朗又好,支那肺炎都好,有咩事發生都唔驚,要鳩縮唔出街都實有得食~~<br />\n當然,,到有日真係出現 全香港範圍MAP炮 就咩都唔使<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Of8f9TL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOf8f9TL.jpg&h=83ab80f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n放在廚房櫃的鑵頭同米,[現鑵頭總存貨有$10000左右]米有50kg<br />\n由歐洲火腿,到中國午餐肉,回煱肉,,豆,菜,金寶湯<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QnFRJdP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQnFRJdP.jpg&h=39128a2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一箱箱未開太多,,放到出廳[依d全部係魚]<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iozfqse.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fiozfqse.jpg&h=6004415d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n水污染,未驚~~~現有16箱 1.5L X12<br />\n其實一向飲樽裝水好耐,現在D水喉水煮完都飲到唔舒服<br />\n即食面 有 5箱左右啦<br />\n<br />\n另外,,打邊爐石油氣有存貨 21支,,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n來吧~~~<br />\n大混亂~~~<br />\n特大災難~~~<br />\n無水~~無電~~無野買的日子呀~~~<br />\n<br />\n期待,手持午餐肉就可以有西屌的日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f28f2eb77cd3c81c17415779cc2aeb6b20ce28ae","tid":1814812,"uid":234527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T05:36:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75c6b4db1069788a0f0d78e090879eccfe6ec37f","tid":1814812,"uid":152147,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T05